&lt;p&gt;The post will be based in the North of Cumbria to support the further development of our pathways. The successful applicant will join a team comprising 3 substantive Consultant Neurologists, a long term locum who visits from overseas, a consultant neurophysiologist. Specialist Nursing support comprises 4.5 MS nurses, 2 epilepsy nurses, 2 PD nurses and 2 general nurses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The posts will involve out-patient and in-patient consultations across North Cumbria. Specific commitments would be agreed in negotiation with colleagues once appointed. The main sites for outpatient clinics is Penrith, with alternate week clinics in Cockermouth. The service currently offers inpatient reviews where required at Cumberland Infirmary and a Consultant of the Week service for telephone advice to GP and consultant colleagues alike within normal office hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 23rd November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
